 Yan et al., 2010; 
 Zhang et al., 2010b; 
 Burns et al., 2013; 
 Luo et al., 2013). As a result, 46 E-30 strains were harvested, with complete EV-like CPE. Subsequently, we randomly selected 32 isolates sampled from different patients for sequencing and phylogenetic analysis (
